"{\n  \"text\": \"Hi everybody. This is real yogurt. I made it on my counter. I used cultures I got in the mail and I grew it out of regular milk that I got the supermarket. It's very different from the yogurt full of probiotic bacteria that you get at the supermarket. Everything in the supermarket is pasteurized in terms of dairy. There is no unpasteurized dairy, that's by law. So anytime you see probiotic bacteria in yogurt, it's just that it's petri dish bacteria that's been injected to the yogurt after it was pasteurized. It was never actually grown there. What you're looking for with beneficial bacteria that helps regrow your gut bacteria is the bacteria that's naturally grown in the dairy. Look for real yogurt. You have to make it yourself, unfortunately. Thanks, y'all. Live better, eat more fermented foods.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hi everybody.\",\n      \"start\": 0.0,\n      \"end\": 1.2,\n      \"duration\": 1.2,\n      \"confidence\": 0.974,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" Hi\",\n          \"start\": 0.0,\n          \"end\": 0.24,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.984\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.72,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 0.72,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \".\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 1.2,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.891\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\": \" This is real yogurt.\",\n      \"start\": 1.2,\n      \"end\": 2.88,\n      \"duration\": 1.68,\n